<h3>Precipitation</h3>
<br><br>
Europe has been wet in November 2017 for northern, central and southeastern Europe (Figure 9 and 10). Some of these areas experienced exceptionally wet conditions and especially in southeastern Europe, the 1-day and 5-day precipitation maxima have been much above the climatological mean value for November. The Iberian peninsula. southwestern France and the UK have been dry or had precipitation amounts near the average value.
